</OrgName>
<Desc><entry>Provides accommodation and support for asylum seekers under the Home Office target accommodation contracts.  Promotes the integration of refugees in the city.  Also has a co-ordination role in relation to EU migrants living in the city, New Arrivals Service (see separate entry).  Runs a drop-in for asylum seekers and refugees which is attended by other agencies such as ASSIST, Red Cross, Refugee Council, Sheffield Futures, Volunteer Centre and the Conversation Club (see separate entries).  Self or any referral.</entry>
</Desc>
